Package: csrtools
Type: Package
Title: What the Package Does (Title Case)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("Becky", "Turner", email = "bectur@ceh.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person("Olivia", "Hartrick", email = "liv.hartrick@ouh.nhs.uk", role = "aut")
  )
Description: crstools provides a workflow for performing meta-analysis and cumulative effect size estimation in R. 
  The package includes functions for calculating and plotting standardised mean change, handling heterogeneity,
  and cumulative meta-analysis with propagated uncertainty estimates. The workflow is particularly suited
  to medical and psychological research applications, allowing researchers to analyse time-series data or
  multiple interventions.
